{"tid":1997643,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［新媒體］連 登 仔 點 睇 癲 狗 日 報 ？！","createTime":"2020-05-01T20:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T21:14:15.000Z","uid":219007,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9fb73e86b736ceab040916290a854785c2421dec","tid":1997643,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T20:06:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/05/02/040543_2f787e21230bcea51eff5f5c77f5c5d8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F05%2F02%2F040543_2f787e21230bcea51eff5f5c77f5c5d8.png&h=590357c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明前幾日問到一條比其他記者尖銳嘅問題，嚇親林鄭月娥都窒左窒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(林奠怒了)記者：會唔會為 遲封關令武漢人由港轉機播毒外國 負責？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日就自己採訪嗰陣無啦啦亂發爛渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tv/B_p79IRheGY/?igshid=1q0xktx9lj0pl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FB_p79IRheGY%2F%3Figshid%3D1q0xktx9lj0pl&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw1%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=fe99b73b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tv/B_p79IRheGY/?igshid=1q0xktx9lj0pl</a><br />\n<br />\n今鋪真係完全整臭自己個朵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b96a62445ec62cc319baaab8f1827b63cbda14","tid":1997643,"uid":31841,"like":5,"dislike":4